<PageLayout
  title="PL-9643: a melanocortin eye drop for dry eye disease"
  kicker="Investigational"
  description="PL-9643 is Palatin's investigational melanocortin eye drop for dry eye disease — the anti-inflammatory arm of the melanocortin system applied straight to the ocular surface. Its Phase 3 MELODY-1 trial met its co-primary symptom endpoint in 2025."
